 Science Stories\"</a>. <i>Goodreads</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">18 October</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Goodreads&amp;rft.atitle=Reading+Science+Stories&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodreads.com%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F25732845-reading-science-stories&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJoy+Hakim\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.educationworld.com/a_curr/curr235.shtml\">\"Education World: Award-Winning History Series Takes Students by Storm! (An ex...\"</a> <i>www.educationworld.com</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">18 October</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=www.educationworld.com&amp;rft.atitle=Education+World%3A+Award-Winning+History+Series+Takes+Students+by+Storm%21+%28An+ex...&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.educationworld.com%2Fa_curr%2Fcurr235.shtml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJoy+Hakim\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-curr235-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-curr235_8-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.education-world.com/a_curr/curr235.shtml\">Award-Winning History Series Takes Students by Storm!</a> Education World e-Interview with author Joy Hakim</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-K12_Website-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-K12_Website_9-0\">^</a></b></